<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ nginx.html_title }}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; margin-top: 100px; background: #f0f8ff; }
        h1 { color: #007bff; }
        .info { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="info">
        <h1>🏠 Bienvenue !</h1>
        <p>Serveur <strong>Nginx</strong> déployé par <strong>Ansible</strong> sur <em>Fedora</em>.</p>
        <p>Hôte : {{ ansible_fqdn }} | IP : {{ ansible_facts["default_ipv4"]["address"] }}</p>
        <p>Déployé le : {{ ansible_date_time.date }}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
